\s Abafundi abaya eEmawusi
\p
\v 13 Futhi khangela, ngalona lolosuku ababili babo babehamba besiya emzaneni, obizo lawo yiEmawusi\x + Mark. 16.12.\x*, \w ongamastadiyu\w** angamatshumi ayisithupha kusukela eJerusalema\x + Joha. 11.18.\x*.
\v 14 Njalo bona babekhulumisana ngazo zonke lezizinto ezenzekileyo.
\v 15 Kwasekusithi bekhulumisana bebuzana, uJesu uqobo wasondela wahamba kanye labo\x + 24.36.\x*,
\v 16 kodwa amehlo abo ayebanjiwe ukuze bangamazi\x + Joha. 20.14.21.4. Luka 24.31.\x*.
\v 17 Wasesithi kubo: Ngamazwi bani la elikhulumisana ngawo lihamba, lidanile\x + Mat. 6.16. Gen. 40.7. Dan. 1.10.\x*?
\v 18 Omunye, obizo lakhe linguKleyopha\x + Joha. 19.25.\x*, wasephendula wathi kuye: Wena nguwe wedwa isihambi eJerusalema, njalo esingaziyo yini izinto ezenzekileyo phakathi kwayo kulezinsuku?
\v 19 Wasesithi kubo: Yizinto bani? Basebesithi kuye: Ezimayelana loJesu weNazaretha, obeyindoda umprofethi\x + Joha. 6.14.\x* olamandla ngesenzo langelizwi phambi kukaNkulunkulu labantu bonke\x + Seb. 7.22. Seb. 2.22.\x*;
\v 20 lokuthi abapristi abakhulu\x + Seb. 2.23. 5.30. 13.27,28.\x* lababusi bethu bamnikela njani ekulahlweni kokufa, bambethela\x + Joha. 3.1.\x*.
\v 21 Kodwa thina besithemba ukuthi nguye obezakhulula uIsrayeli\x + 1.68. 2.38. Seb. 1.6.\x*. Kodwa-ke phezu kwakho konke lokhu lamuhla lusuku lwesithathu selokhu lezizinto zenzakele.
\v 22 Kodwa njalo abesifazana abathile abangakithi basimangalisile\x + Mat. 28.1,8. Mark. 16.1,2,10. Joha. 20.18.\x*, ababesengcwabeni ekuseni kakhulu\x + 24.1.\x*;
\v 23 kuthe bengasitholi isidumbu sakhe\x + 24.3.\x*, babuya besithi babone lombono wezingilosi\x + 24.4.\x*, ezithe uyaphila\x + 24.5-7.\x*.
\v 24 Labathile abebelathi baya engcwabeni, bafica kunjalo njengokutsho kwabesifazana labo; kodwa yena kabambonanga\x + 24.12. Joha. 20.3.\x*.
\v 25 Yena wasesithi kubo: O lina elingelakuqedisisa elilenhliziyo ezivilaphela ukukholwa konke lokho abaprofethi abakutshoyo!
